OL,9,G2310F24 Hours in A&E
OL,10,     GThis episode meets patients whose
OL,11,     Gvisions of the world are rocked
OL,12,     Gby life-changing events. Sergio,
OL,13,     Gwho's 44, and Alan, who's 71,
OL,14,     Ghave both been badly injured in
OL,15,     Gcycling accidents.
OL,16,G0015F999: On the Front Line
OL,17,     GParamedics treat a woman with a
OL,18,     Gbroken leg, a man who's passed
OL,19,     Gout in the street, a woman who's
OL,20,     Ghad a seizure on a bus, and a man
OL,21,     Gwho's collapsed in his bathroom.
